Specifications:

We need to create
  1. One Python file (Backend)
  2. Two HTML files  (Frontend)
  3. One CSS file    (Frontend)

We need to install Flask and Folium

Flask: It is a web server gateway interface application in python. This is used for developing web apps.
command to install Flask: pip install flask.

Folium: It is a python API for visualizing data. It is a good API to include map related visualizations.
command to install Folium: pip install folium.

